metadata.title: Database of Pink and Chum Salmon Scale, Body Size Measurements and Survival Patterns

creators.name: University of Alaska Fairbanks (UAF), School of Fisheries

metadata.description:
Salmon stocks from North Pacific as well as Japan, Russia and Alaska, collecting also body size database and survival database.  50 males and females will be viewed equally.
An NPMR project
